name: Soul ice cream: pistachio vanilla
description:
I don’t like to tell you what you need to see, I don’t like to comment on my creations because I could write a book about each, and in the end everything is just what you see and feel, the reflection of your current level of consciousness.

Soul ice cream is a metaphor for compressed telepathic information packages of the spirit, received in a form of a feeling, as if you’d taste most delicious ice creams. You can’t experience an ice cream reading its ingredients, but only if you taste it. The meaning of all life in this endless multiverse is, to reach and join a higher level of consciousness. This is the general and eternal algorithm, every single particle strives in this direction.
